narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned how to write college-level papers and useful skills of organization that I will use for the rest of my papers throughout college. I also learned of several historical events and perspectives on social injustices that I was unaware of before.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I really enjoyed how interactive class was and how much discussion there was. I have no weaknesses.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, I would. The skills acquired for writing are going to be very useful for the rest of my time here at Yale and well after. Additionally, this course is a great way to improve writing skills while learning about important and interesting events.
